ğŸŸª EPIC â€“ Return Hardware â€“ Layout & Navigation Framework

Objective

Provide a consistent and persistent layout framework for the Return Hardware journey, ensuring that coaches are guided through each step with clear navigation, visibility of progress, and a standardized user experience across all screens.

Description

This epic covers all structural and persistent UI components used across the Return Hardware process, independently of the business logic of each step.

It includes:
	â€¢	A fixed header identifying the process
	â€¢	A non-clickable stepper showing progress
	â€¢	A persistent action bar with BACK and NEXT navigation
	â€¢	Consistent behavior across all steps, including error states (modal/toast)

The goal is to provide a solid UI foundation so that each functional step only focuses on its own business content.

Business Value
	â€¢	Improves coach experience and clarity
	â€¢	Reduces navigation errors
	â€¢	Standardizes guided processes
	â€¢	Speeds up development of future similar journeys (Onboarding, Exchange, etc.)
	â€¢	Ensures UI consistency and robustness

