ğŸŸ¦ US1 â€“ Display a non-clickable stepper for the Return Hardware process

User Story

As a coach
I want to see a stepper showing all steps of the Return Hardware process
So that I clearly understand where I am and what remains to be done

Description

A stepper is displayed on all screens of the Return Hardware journey.
It contains exactly 5 steps, in the following order:
	1.	Owner Search
	2.	Equipment Selection
	3.	Form Filling
	4.	Return Summary
	5.	Signature & Confirmation

The stepper:
	â€¢	Highlights the current step
	â€¢	Marks completed steps
	â€¢	Displays upcoming steps as inactive
	â€¢	Is not clickable
	â€¢	Is always visible throughout the journey

Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN I am in the Return Hardware process
WHEN the screen is displayed
THEN a stepper with 5 steps is visible

WHEN a step is active
THEN it is visually highlighted

WHEN a step is completed
THEN it is displayed as completed

WHEN I click on a step in the stepper
THEN no navigation occurs

THEN the stepper remains visible on all steps of the journey

