ğŸŸ¦ US2 â€“ Display a fixed header with the process title

User Story

As a coach
I want to see a fixed header displaying the process title
So that I always know which process I am currently in

Description

A fixed header is displayed at the top of every screen of the Return Hardware journey.

The exact title displayed is:

RETURN HARDWARE PROCESS

The header:
	â€¢	Is always visible
	â€¢	Does not disappear between steps
	â€¢	Remains visible even when errors occur (modal or toast)
	â€¢	Follows the validated UI design

Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN I am in the Return Hardware process
THEN a fixed header displaying "RETURN HARDWARE PROCESS" is visible

THEN the header remains visible on all steps

WHEN an error modal or toast is displayed
THEN the header remains visible

